Articles.Content:
Welcome to Tylo Project Episode 1! We join our interplanetary transfer vehicle in low-Kerbin orbit (as I forgot to actually record its launch, if you want to see one launch, watch any other Project 1 episode). We then launch our Tylo Lander. It has a Nerva engine to dominate the terrible moon. We dock them together, head over to Jool, aerobrake into an orbit, and get an interaction with Tylo. Tomorrow, we undock, land, plant a flag, and get back into orbit.

Full Length

Highlights

Here is Tylo Project Episode 2! We undock, land on Tylo, plant a flag, and head back into a low Tylo orbit. Tomorrow, we re-dock, head home, and land back on Kerbin!

Full Length

Highlights

Welcome to Tylo Project Episode 3! Today, we dock our lander and interplanetary transfer vehicle together in low Tylo orbit, transfer crew back from the lander, ditch the lander, burn into an orbit around Jool, set a course for Kerbin, head home, and land amongst the trees!

Thanks for watching!
